All heroes start somewhere and for Courtney Whitmore, it all began when she moved from L.A. to Blue Valley Nebraska with her mom and Stepfather Pat Dugan. After Courtney finds a cosmic belt that imbues her with superpowers, it puts her on a collision course with Pat, whose mysterious past may answer why crazy things keep happening in Blue Valley. Join us as we read the first run of Stars and S.T.R.I.P.E., a truly heartwarming romp written by Geoff Johns as a way to immortalize his sister. Grab your Converter Belt, get your big robot online, and get ready for a crash course in the DC Universe in this fun-filled recap of the early days of Stargirl!

